title: MAGIX Music Maker 2014 Premium 20.0.4.49 [ChingLiu]
description:
Changes in Version 20.0.4.49 compared to 20.0.3.45:

-Errors during reopening of MP3 files in the project have been fixed
-Error in Play Solo in the Object FX Rack have been fixed
-Closing of Mastering Suite and the Master Audio Effect Rack again possible using shortcuts and menu items
-Shortcuts after BPM adjustment work again
-Esc closes the mixer
-Welcome dialog has been optimized
-Localization erros for EN and IT have been corrected
-Object synthesizers no longer disappear behind the arranger
-Wasapi settings are correctly saved
-Peak meter update in monitor has been improved
-Harmony Bar in the arranger is correctly updated
-Effects in old projects are loaded correctly
-Use of Vita Instruments has been optimized
-Vintage Organ performance has been improved

Minimum System Requirements

- Microsoft Windows XP, Vista, 7, 8
- Processor: 2 GHz or higher
- RAM: 1 GB (2 GB recommended)
- Graphics card: Onboard graphics card with a screen resolution of at least 1024 x 768
- Sound card: Internal sound card
- Hard disk memory: 9 GB free disk space for program installation
- Optical drive: DVD drive (only for installation of the box version)
- Internet connection: An Internet connection is required to activate the software

Language : English
